c: 2
v: 135
t: "Wong Yahudi lan wong Nashara padha ngucap marang wong mukmin: \"Sira padha mlebu agama Yahudi utawa Agama Nasrani mesti sira padha oleh pituduh\". (Muhammad) sira maringanan wangsulan: \"Kita malah padha nderek agamane Ibrahim, kang akeh lerege bener, lan Ibrahim dudu ewoning wong Musyrik"